tags.text:
CustomElement

A custom element extends upon a regular HTMLElement but adds fields for describing and wrapping a widget constructor.
getWidgetConstructor Return the widget constructor for this element
getDescriptor        Return the element descriptor for this element
getWidgetInstance    Return the widget instance that this element wraps
setWidgetInstance    Set the widget instance for this element

CustomElementAttributeDescriptor

Describes a custom element attribute
attributeName   The name of the attribute on the DOM element
propertyName    The name of the property on the widget
value           A function that takes a string or null value, and returns a new value. The widget's property will be set to the new value.

CustomElementDescriptor

Describes a custom element.
tagName             The tag name to register this widget under. Tag names must contain a "-"
widgetConstructor   widget Constructor that will return the widget to be wrapped in a custom element
attributes          A list of attributes to define on this element
properties          A list of properties to define on this element
events              A list of events to expose on this element
initialization      A method to run to set custom properties on the wrapped widget
